{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Tit|2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","chapter":2,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":1,"text":"But you are to proclaim things consistent with sound teaching.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":2,"text":"Older men are to be self-controlled, worthy of respect, sensible, and sound in faith, love, and endurance.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":3,"text":"In the same way, older women are to be reverent in behavior, not slanderers, not slaves to excessive drinking. They are to teach what is good,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":4,"text":"so that they may encourage the young women to love their husbands and to love their children,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":5,"text":"to be self-controlled, pure, workers at home, kind, and in submission to their husbands, so that God’s word will not be slandered.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":6,"text":"In the same way, encourage the young men to be self-controlled","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":7,"text":"in everything. Make yourself an example of good works with integrity and dignity in your teaching.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":8,"text":"Your message is to be sound beyond reproach, so that any opponent will be ashamed, because he doesn’t have anything bad to say about us.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":9,"text":"Slaves are to submit to their masters in everything, and to be well-pleasing, not talking back","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":10,"text":"or stealing, but demonstrating utter faithfulness, so that they may adorn the teaching of God our Savior in everything.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":11,"text":"For the grace of God has appeared, bringing salvation for all people,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":12,"text":"instructing us to deny godlessness and worldly lusts and to live in a sensible, righteous, and godly way in the present age,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":13,"text":"while we wait for the blessed hope, the appearing of the glory of our great God and Savior, Jesus Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Tit:2:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Tit","bookOrder":55,"chapter":2,"verse":14,"text":"He gave himself for us to redeem us from all lawlessness and to cleanse for himself a pe